# Framer Motion

> Production-ready motion library for React. Declarative animations with gesture support, layout animations, and server-side rendering compatibility.

---

## Overview

Framer Motion simplifies complex animations in React:
- **Declarative syntax** — Animate with props, not imperative code
- **Gesture support** — Drag, hover, tap, pan, scroll
- **Layout animations** — Automatic transitions when elements move
- **Exit animations** — AnimatePresence for unmounting animations
- **Server-safe** — Works with Next.js and SSR

### Why Framer Motion?

| Feature | Benefit |
|---------|---------|
| **Simple API** | `<motion.div animate={{x: 100}} />` |
| **Spring physics** | Natural-feeling animations |
| **Variants** | Orchestrated multi-element animations |
| **Layout** | Automatic position/size transitions |
| **Gestures** | Built-in drag, hover, tap |

